<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>SiteHunter — Encontre clientes. Feche vendas. Cresça.</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=Outfit:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --green: #00e87a;
    --green-dim: #00b85f;
    --dark: #080b0f;
    --card: #0f1318;
    --border: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    --text: #e8edf3;
    --muted: #6b7785;
    --font-display: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif;
    --font-body: 'Outfit', sans-serif;
  }

  html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }

  body {
    background: var(--dark);
    color: var(--text);
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.6;
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  /* ─── NOISE TEXTURE ─── */
  body::before {
    content: '';
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.03'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 0;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  /* ─── NAV ─── */
  nav {
    position: fixed;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    z-index: 100;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    padding: 20px 40px;
    background: rgba(8,11,15,0.85);
    backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .logo {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 28px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #fff;
  }
  .logo span { color: var(--green); }

  .nav-cta {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #000;
    border: none;
    padding: 10px 24px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }
  .nav-cta:hover { background: #fff; transform: translateY(-1px); }

  /* ─── HERO ─── */
  .hero {
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 120px 24px 80px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .hero-glow {
    position: absolute;
    top: 20%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 600px;
    height: 600px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,232,122,0.12) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    background: rgba(0,232,122,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,232,122,0.3);
    border-radius: 50px;
    padding: 6px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s ease both;
  }

  .badge-dot {
    width: 7px; height: 7px;
    background: var(--green);
    border-radius: 50%;
    animation: pulse 1.5s ease infinite;
  }

  @keyframes pulse {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
    50% { opacity: 0.4; transform: scale(0.7); }
  }

  h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(64px, 10vw, 130px);
    line-height: 0.95;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #fff;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.1s ease both;
    max-width: 900px;
  }

  h1 .accent { color: var(--green); }

  .hero-sub {
    font-size: clamp(16px, 2vw, 20px);
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin: 24px auto 0;
    font-weight: 400;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.2s ease both;
  }

  /* ─── WAITLIST FORM ─── */
  .form-wrap {
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-top: 40px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.3s ease both;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .form-wrap input {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 14px 20px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 15px;
    width: 280px;
    outline: none;
    transition: border 0.2s;
  }
  .form-wrap input::placeholder { color: var(--muted); }
  .form-wrap input:focus { border-color: var(--green); }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #000;
    border: none;
    padding: 14px 28px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 15px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover { background: #fff; transform: translateY(-2px); box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0,232,122,0.25); }

  .hero-note {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 14px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.4s ease both;
  }

  .hero-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 48px;
    margin-top: 64px;
    animation: fadeUp 0.6s 0.5s ease both;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .stat {
    text-align: center;
  }
  .stat-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 42px;
    color: #fff;
    display: block;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .stat-num span { color: var(--green); }
  .stat-label {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 4px;
  }

  /* ─── SECTION BASE ─── */
  section {
    padding: 100px 24px;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--green);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(40px, 5vw, 72px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .section-sub {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 560px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ─── PROBLEM ─── */
  .problem { background: var(--dark); }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .problem-card {
    background: var(--card);
    padding: 40px;
    transition: background 0.3s;
  }
  .problem-card:hover { background: #141920; }

  .problem-icon {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: block;
  }

  .problem-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .problem-text {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ─── HOW IT WORKS ─── */
  .how { background: #090c10; }

  .steps {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
    gap: 32px;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .step {
    position: relative;
    padding: 36px;
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, transform 0.3s;
  }
  .step:hover { border-color: rgba(0,232,122,0.3); transform: translateY(-4px); }

  .step-num {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 80px;
    color: rgba(0,232,122,0.08);
    line-height: 1;
    position: absolute;
    top: 16px;
    right: 24px;
  }

  .step-icon {
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    background: rgba(0,232,122,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,232,122,0.25);
    border-radius: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 22px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .step-title {
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 18px;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .step-text {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ─── FEATURES ─── */
  .features { background: var(--dark); }

  .features-layout {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 60px;
    align-items: center;
    margin-top: 60px;
  }

  .feature-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .feature-item {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
    border-radius: 12px;
    border: 1px solid transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.3s, background 0.3s;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .feature-item:hover {
    background: var(--card);
    border-color: var(--border);
  }

  .feature-check {
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    background: rgba(0,232,122,0.15);
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-top: 2px;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .feature-title {
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .feature-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  /* Fake UI mockup */
  .mockup {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 40px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
  }

  .mockup-bar {
    background: #0d1117;
    padding: 14px 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .dot { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .dot-r { background: #ff5f57; }
  .dot-y { background: #ffbd2e; }
  .dot-g { background: #28ca41; }

  .mockup-body { padding: 24px; }

  .mock-search {
    background: #0d1117;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .mock-map {
    background: #0d1117;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    height: 130px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .mock-map::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 0px, transparent 1px, transparent 30px),
      repeating-linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.02) 0px, transparent 1px, transparent 30px);
  }

  .map-pin {
    position: absolute;
    width: 10px; height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--green);
    box-shadow: 0 0 12px var(--green);
    animation: blink 2s ease infinite;
  }

  @keyframes blink {
    0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
    50% { opacity: 0.3; }
  }

  .map-pin:nth-child(1) { top: 30%; left: 35%; animation-delay: 0s; }
  .map-pin:nth-child(2) { top: 55%; left: 60%; animation-delay: 0.5s; }
  .map-pin:nth-child(3) { top: 20%; left: 70%; animation-delay: 1s; }
  .map-pin:nth-child(4) { top: 65%; left: 25%; animation-delay: 1.5s; background: rgba(0,232,122,0.4); }

  .mock-label {
    position: absolute;
    top: 8px; left: 12px;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .mock-results {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 8px;
  }

  .mock-result-item {
    background: #0d1117;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mock-biz-name {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .mock-biz-cat {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-top: 2px;
  }

  .mock-badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 3px 8px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .mock-badge.no-site {
    background: rgba(0,232,122,0.15);
    color: var(--green);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,232,122,0.3);
  }

  /* ─── PRICING ─── */
  .pricing { background: #090c10; }

  .plans {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
    margin-top: 60px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .plan {
    background: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 36px;
    position: relative;
    transition: transform 0.3s;
  }
  .plan:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); }

  .plan.featured {
    border-color: var(--green);
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f1a13 0%, var(--card) 100%);
  }

  .plan-featured-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: -12px;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    background: var(--green);
    color: #000;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    padding: 4px 16px;
    border-radius: 50px;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .plan-name {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .plan-price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 56px;
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1;
  }
  .plan-price .currency { font-size: 24px; color: var(--muted); vertical-align: top; margin-top: 10px; display: inline-block; }
  .plan-price .period { font-family: var(--font-body); font-size: 15px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; }

  .plan-desc {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin: 16px 0 24px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .plan-divider {
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .plan-items {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 12px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .plan-items li {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: var(--text);
    display: flex;
    gap: 10px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .plan-items li::before {
    content: '✓';
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 700;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    font-size: 13px;
    margin-top: 1px;
  }

  .plan-btn {
    display: block;
    text-align: center;
    padding: 14px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 14px;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    width: 100%;
  }
  .plan-btn.outline {
    background: transparent;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  .plan-btn.outline:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }
  .plan-btn.solid {
    background: var(--green);
    color: #000;
  }
  .plan-btn.solid:hover { background: #fff; }

  /* ─── CTA FINAL ─── */
  .cta-final {
    background: var(--dark);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-box {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0d1a12 0%, #0a1015 50%, #0d1a12 100%);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,232,122,0.2);
    border-radius: 24px;
    padding: 80px 40px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .cta-box::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: -100px; left: 50%;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    width: 400px; height: 400px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,232,122,0.1) 0%, transparent 70%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-box h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(48px, 6vw, 86px);
    line-height: 1;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
    color: #fff;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .cta-box p {
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--muted);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }

  /* ─── FOOTER ─── */
  footer {
    padding: 40px 24px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
  }

  footer p {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--muted);
  }

  /* ─── ANIMATIONS ─── */
  @keyframes fadeUp {
    from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
    to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  }

  .reveal {
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(30px);
    transition: opacity 0.7s ease, transform 0.7s ease;
  }
  .reveal.visible {
    opacity: 1;
    transform: translateY(0);
  }

  /* ─── SUCCESS STATE ─── */
  .success-msg {
    display: none;
    color: var(--green);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin-top: 16px;
  }

  /* ─── RESPONSIVE ─── */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    nav { padding: 16px 20px; }
    .features-layout { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .mockup { display: none; }
    footer { flex-direction: column; text-align: center; }
    .hero-stats { gap: 32px; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav>
  <div class="logo">SITE<span>HUNTER</span></div>
  <a href="#waitlist" class="nav-cta">Entrar na lista</a>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-glow"></div>

  <div class="badge">
    <span class="badge-dot"></span>
    Lançamento em breve — vagas limitadas
  </div>

  <h1>ENCONTRE.<br><span class="accent">FECHE.</span><br>CRESÇA.</h1>

  <p class="hero-sub">
    A primeira plataforma brasileira que mostra exatamente quais negócios perto de você ainda não têm site — e te dá tudo pra fechar a venda.
  </p>

  <div class="form-wrap" id="waitlist">
    <input type="email" id="emailInput" placeholder="Seu melhor e-mail" autocomplete="email">
    <button class="btn-primary" onclick="handleWaitlist()">Garantir minha vaga →</button>
  </div>
  <div class="success-msg" id="successMsg">✓ Incrível! Te avisamos quando abrir. Fique de olho no e-mail.</div>
  <p class="hero-note">100% gratuito na fase beta. Sem cartão de crédito.</p>

  <div class="hero-stats">
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">+<span>7M</span></span>
      <div class="stat-label">negócios no Brasil sem site</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num"><span>R$</span>0</span>
      <div class="stat-label">pra começar a prospectar</div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat">
      <span class="stat-num">3<span>x</span></span>
      <div class="stat-label">mais clientes por semana</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- PROBLEM -->
<section class="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">O problema</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Freelancer bom que é bom<br>não falta. Cliente falta.</h2>
    <p class="section-sub reveal">Você sabe criar sites, mas onde estão os clientes? Essa é a dor de 90% dos freelancers.</p>

    <div class="problem-grid reveal">
      <div class="problem-card">
        <span class="problem-icon">😮‍💨</span>
        <div class="problem-title">Horas buscando cliente no escuro</div>
        <p class="problem-text">Você manda mensagem aleatória, manda proposta no ar, e fica esperando. Sem método. Sem direção.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <span class="problem-icon">🗺️</span>
        <div class="problem-title">Não sabe quem precisa de site</div>
        <p class="problem-text">Tem negócio sem site na próxima rua. Você só não sabe qual é. Essa informação deveria ser óbvia.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="problem-card">
        <span class="problem-icon">🤐</span>
        <div class="problem-title">Na hora de vender, trava</div>
        <p class="problem-text">Achou o cliente, mas não sabe o que falar, como abordar, como mandar uma proposta que convença.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

